fields.name: Clarity
fields.meaning: Birch is the tree of renewal and new beginnings. It clears the path forward and invites fresh vision after darkness.

fields.name: Endurance
fields.meaning: Oak is the tree of strength and perseverance. Rooted deep, it withstands storms and grows stronger with time.

fields.name: Vitality
fields.meaning: Redwood is the tree of resilience and life force. It rises high from fire and hardship, carrying the spirit of renewal.

fields.name: Illumination
fields.meaning: Yew is the tree of spirit and eternal transformation. It bridges the seen and unseen, offering quiet, enduring wisdom.

fields.name: Reflection
fields.meaning: Willow is the tree of emotional flow and healing. It bends but does not break, guiding you to embrace your inner tides.
